description:
&lt;p&gt;A short term Recruitment and retention premium of £3,061 will be applied to this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Eastbourne DGH has a busy thriving Endoscopy unit. We have a new state of the art JAG accredited purpose built department which provides Endoscopy procedures to inpatient and outpatients under taking both diagnostic and therapeutic procedures. We work closely with our clinicians to provide a patient focused service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This exciting opportunity has risen for highly motivated and enthusiastic registered nurses to join our innovative team. Our evolving department offers a superb Endoscopy specific training programme. The successful applicant will have a six week supernumerary/induction plan. We are committed to providing staff with learning and development opportunities to support their career progression.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Danielle Lloyd&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward Matron&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;0300 131 4500 ext 136743/134215&lt;/p&gt;
